What is Time Logger? 
Time logger is a complete organizational solution to record developers time and get their development tasks done. With the built-in time tracking features, you can easily record the hours that you put in. 
 
Timer Extension for Google Chrome
With the Time Tracker extension, turn on a timer whenever you get to work, and stop the 
timer when you're done. You can also manually log time after you are done with your work, or 
view and edit all your recent time entries right from the extension.
